        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/31138",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=dotvoid",
                        "name": "dotvoid",
                        "displayName": "Danne Lundqvist",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It seems that there is no translator returned in the label decorator for file elements. The method called is Zend_Form_Element_File::getTranslator() which in the end is calling Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract::getTranslator()\n\nThe code in Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract does not return the default translator if there is not a specific one assigned. Replacing the code in Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract::getTranslator() with the below (from Zend_Form_Element::getTranslator()) fixes the problem and make sure the default translators is returned.\n\n        if ($this->translatorIsDisabled()) {\n            return null;\n        }\n\n        if (null === $this->_translator) {\n            require_once 'Zend\/Form.php';\n            return Zend_Form::getDefaultTranslator();\n        }\n        return $this->_translator;",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=dotvoid",
                        "name": "dotvoid",
                        "displayName": "Danne Lundqvist",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-05-19T08:02:41.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-05-19T08:02:41.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/31153",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bate",
                        "name": "bate",
                        "displayName": "Marco Kaiser",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "added patch for this issue",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=bate",
                        "name": "bate",
                        "displayName": "Marco Kaiser",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-05-19T13:35:50.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-05-19T13:35:50.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/32133",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=digitalstruct",
                        "name": "digitalstruct",
                        "displayName": "Mike Willbanks",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I don't believe that adding the form translator into the Zend_File_Transfer_Adapter_Abstract is the correct fix for this.  It would seem that it would be a better fix to put this into the Zend_Form_Element_File area and setting it from there rather than adding additional complexity and coupling the File_Transfer_Adapter to the form.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=digitalstruct",
                        "name": "digitalstruct",
                        "displayName": "Mike Willbanks",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-06-23T18:24:06.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-06-23T18:24:06.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/32134",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=digitalstruct",
                        "name": "digitalstruct",
                        "displayName": "Mike Willbanks",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I cannot reproduce this bug in the trunk:\n\n{code}\n        require_once 'Zend\/Translate.php';\n        $translate = new Zend_Translate('array', array('foo' => 'bar'), 'en');\n\n        Zend_Form::setDefaultTranslator($translate);\n        $form = new Zend_Form();\n        $element = new Zend_Form_Element_File('file');\n        $element->setLabel('foo');\n        $form->addElement($element);\n        $form->setView(new Zend_View());\n\n        $html = (string) $form;\n{code}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=digitalstruct",
                        "name": "digitalstruct",
                        "displayName": "Mike Willbanks",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-06-23T18:53:59.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-06-23T18:53:59.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/32154",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Confirmed Mike's diagnosis -- on trunk, this is working fine. Closing; re-open if you can provide reproduce code off of current trunk that shows labels not being translated.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-06-24T09:18:16.000+0000",
